location.fullValue: Hayward Plan, High Point at Foxbank

data.description: This home is beautifully appointed! Just 15 minutes from Lake Moultrie centrally located between Goose Creek and Moncks Corner! Gourmet Kitchen w/ double ovens, gas cooktop, dishwasher, silestone countertops and upgraded cabinets. Custom ceiling mounted flush Yamaha speakers throughout the house! Living room has 5 speakers for true surround sound, 2 more additional ones outside. Master bathroom has a single flush speaker as well. All wires run to one outlet for easy hookup of your multi room receiver. Deluxe primary suite with separate shower and tub, double bowl sinks, and tray ceiling in primary bedroom. Fully fenced in backyard with custom rear patio with outdoor brick fireplace, great for entertaining nights! You will also love the flex space upstairs that is a great secondary living room or a great office or media room in addition to the secondary bedrooms also upstairs.  Walk to the dog park, pool, playground, lake dock & Foxbank Elementary School.  The firestation is also located in the community right next to the school.  At the entrance to the community is a gas station, restaurants, coffee shop, fitness center with more planned to come!  Don't miss out and schedule your showing now!
